notes: Drinks: Afgh: 56 runs/ 3 wkts, after 18.3 overs, 4ex, 8x4 0x6.
Mohammad Nabi: 50 runs in 33minutes, from 28 balls, 3x4 3x6
Samiullah S: 51 runs off 72 balls in 97 minutes 2x4 1x6
Sikandar Raza retired hurt on 38* from 89/2 to 205/4

milestones.description: Dawlat Zadran has broken the record for most ducks (3) in ODIs for AFG, going past Shapoor's 3
Mohammad Nabi has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (34) for AFG, going past Samiullah Shinwari
